text: Wayne's World 2 is a 1993 American comedy movie from Paramount Pictures, starring Mike Myers and Dana Carvey. It is based on a segment of the same name from television's Saturday Night Live. ==Other websites== * Category:1993 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies based on TV series Category:Movies set in Illinois Category:Self-reflexive movies Category:Screenplays by Mike Myers Category:Multilingual movies
